eu.diversify.trio.builder

Interface TrioListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TrioBaseListener

    public interface TrioListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by TrioParser.
